eal of prejudice and hatred in <LOCATION> Dade </LOCATION> <LOCATION> County </LOCATION>, and this act shows that more integration between Anglos, blacks, Hispanics, Jews and gentiles needs to take place,'' said <PERSON> Barry </PERSON> <PERSON> Tabachnikoff </PERSON>, rabbi at the 450-member Bet Breira Congregation. `` We still have a lot of work to do, especially in the religious community.''
