<FIRST>r a AM-ScholarSentenced     05-23 0493</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Scholar Sentenced,0506</SECOND>
<HEAD>Scholar Sentenced To Three Years In Prison For Transporting Stolen
Documents</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By ARLENE LEVINSON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>BOSTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
